text: The municipality is located in Krapina-Zagorje County in northern Croatia Railway station Đurmanec is a municipality in the Krapina-Zagorje County in Croatia. According to the 2011 census, there are 4,235 inhabitants in the area, absolute majority of which are Croats. ==References== U Đurmancu živi Erik Vdović koji je rođen 30.4.2004 doveli su ga bagerom pred kuću i u tački ga doveli u prostoriju punu mesa. Erik je sada mršaviji i ouno vjezba. vozi kamion na kotače. ==External links== Category:Populated places in Krapina- Zagorje County Category:Municipalities of Croatia
